						<summary>

						<p>This records an agreement among the artisans of all parts of Koṅgumaṇḍalam to give an impost of one <hi rend="italic">paṇam</hi> in coin and a specified quantity of corn in kind levied on each family, for the renovation of the temples of Siṅga-Perumāḷ and Paḷḷikoṇḍa-Perumāḷ at Tiruvā[lu]ttalam.</p>						

						</summary>
